source: TEXT_HEAVNZ914_01979_SEQ_00<tab>The Allagan training node is silently awaiting user interaction.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ914_01979_SEQ_00<tab>La sphère d'en<var 16 /var>traî<var 16 /var>ne<var 16 /var>ment attend sagement son utilisateur.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ914_01979_SEQ_01<tab>Mistaking you for an Allagan soldier, the training node instructs you to locate and defeat five snapper-rooks as part of standard daily Allagan military training.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ914_01979_SEQ_01<tab>Vous prenant à tort pour un soldat allagois, la sphère d'en<var 16 /var>traî<var 16 /var>ne<var 16 /var>ment vous a donné l'ordre de trouver et d'éliminer cinq <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 0DF20DCC0302 /var> dans le quadrant alpha, un exercice standard de la formation militaire allagoise.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ914_01979_SEQ_02<tab>You have destroyed the snapper-rooks as instructed. Notify the training node that you have completed the assigned task.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ914_01979_SEQ_02<tab>Vous avez détruit les <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 0DF20DCC0302 /var>. Transmettez cette information à la sphère d'en<var 16 /var>traî<var 16 /var>ne<var 16 /var>ment, à l'Hélice.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ914_01979_SEQ_03<tab>The training node explains to you the importance of the task it set you, but the message is so distorted by static that you fail to discern what it is trying to tell you.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ914_01979_SEQ_03<tab>La sphère d'en<var 16 /var>traî<var 16 /var>ne<var 16 /var>ment vous a expliqué l'importance de l'exercice du jour, mais le message était quasiment inaudible et vous n'avez pas compris ce qu'elle essayait de vous dire.
TEXT_HEAVNZ914_01979_TODO_01<tab>Faire un rapport à la sphère d'en<var 16 /var>traî<var 16 /var>ne<var 16 /var>ment

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ914_01979_TRAININGSYSTEM_000_000<tab>Greetings, loyal soldiers of the Allagan Empire. Today's training regimen starts now.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ914_01979_TRAININGSYSTEM_000_000<tab>Salutations, loyaux soldats de l'empire d'Allag. L'en<var 16 /var>traî<var 16 /var>ne<var 16 /var>ment du jour va commencer.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ914_01979_TRAININGSYSTEM_000_001<tab>Your task is to locate and destroy <var 1A 02 /var>FIVE SNAPPER-ROOKS<var 1A 01 /var>. Please ensure that all targets are rendered completely dead and/or inoperable. Good hunting, soldiers.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ914_01979_TRAININGSYSTEM_000_001<tab>Votre tâche est de repérer et de détruire cinq <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 0DF20DCC0302 /var>. Veuillez faire en sorte que toutes les cibles soient bien inopérantes. Bonne chasse, soldats.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ914_01979_TRAININGSYSTEM_000_010<tab>Locate and destroy <var 1A 02 /var>FIVE SNAPPER-ROOKS<var 1A 01 /var>. Please ensure that all targets are rendered completely dead and/or inoperable.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ914_01979_TRAININGSYSTEM_000_010<tab>Repérez et détruisez cinq <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 0DF20DCC0302 /var>. Veuillez faire en sorte que toutes les cibles soient bien inopérantes.
TEXT_HEAVNZ914_01979_TRAININGSYSTEM_000_020<tab>Fé<var 16 /var>li<var 16 /var>ci<var 16 /var>ta<var 16 /var>tions. Vous avez réussi à... bzzzzzzz... exercice du jour.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ914_01979_TRAININGSYSTEM_000_021<tab>Today's training is intended to teach the importance of...<buzzzzzz>...when dealing...<buzzzzzz>...situations. We hope this knowledge serves you well in your service of the Allagan Empire.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ914_01979_TRAININGSYSTEM_000_021<tab>L'exercice du jour est destiné à montrer l'importance... bzzzz... quand il s'agit de... bzzzzzz... situations. Gloire à l'empire d'Allag, et longue vie à Sa Majesté Xande<var 1D /var>!
